'''Devǎnagǎrī''' si yekh [[abugida]] [[lekhipen]] labyardo te lekhavel, korkoro vai le avere lekhimatenca, chhiba andar o [[Indikano Subkontinento]] sar [[sanskritikani]], [[hindi]], [[marathi]], [[kashmiri]], [[sindhi]], [[romani]], [[bihari]], [[bhili]], [[konkani]], [[bhojpuri]], [[nepali]].

== Nav ==
I devǎnagǎrī sas kerdini ando 12-to [[shelbersh]] andar o lekhipen [[Siddham]]. Pe sanskritikani, ''nagǎrī'' si i juvlikani forma andar ''nāgara'' (forutno). Si juvlikani andar kodya so pasharel i juvlikani navni ''lipi'' (lekhipen) , thai ''devǎ'' si "devel": ''devǎnagǎrī lipi'' - "forutno lekhipen le devlenge".

== Sar lekhavel pe ==

Pe devǎnagǎri lekhipen si 12 ''svǎra'' (vokalurya) thai 34 ''vyǎnjǎna'' (konsonanturya). 

=== Vyǎnjǎna ===
O devǎnagǎrī lekhipen si ek ''abugida'' lekhipen andar kodya so sa le vyǎnjǎna kana si korkore si len o svǎr ''ǎ''. Sar misalyake, o grafem "प" si "pǎ". Te avel "p" trebul te labyardyovel o [[viram]] "्" so sikavel ke "ǎ" perel: "प्" si "p". 

O ''viram'' nai labyardo te sikavel ke "ǎ" perel kana dui vai buteder vyǎnjǎna si ek palal avreste, bisvǎrenge mashkar lenge. Atunch, le pasharde vyǎnjǎna phanden pen, kerindoi ekh phandipen. Sar misalyake, "k" lekhavdyovel korkoro sar "क्" thai "l" si korkoro "ल्". Ekh palal avreste si "क्ल्". Kathe o "क्" xasardyas i chachi rig. Numa o paluno vyǎnjǎn achhel bichhindo, sar misalyake trin vyǎnjǎna ekh palal avreste: "ख्स्त" si "khst" thai korkore si "ख", "स", "त". Si buteder regule te keren pen le vyǎnjǎnenge phandipena. Acharutnes, kana varekon lekhavel pe compyuter dosta te thol o viram/विराम "्" mashkar lende te keren pen le phandipena automatikanes. Sar misalyake, kerindoi klik "ग" + "्" + "ल" avel "ग्ल".

Tele si le vyǎnjǎna andar o devǎnagǎrī lekhipen. 

